@Comment:	Time is 0:04
@Comment:	Chi eats dinner with his Mother , his mother's boyfriend , his little brother who is five and a half , and his little sister who is three and a half. This family is very talkative and everyone likes to interrupt each other; they all seem very involved in the conversation. Most of the time their attention is focused on a lunar eclipse which is occuring; the boyfriend offers a nice explanation which seems to be a little too complicated for the children.
